summary: Prompt: “Do you have any idea what I want to do to you?” Pairing: Crowley x Reader You slid your angel blade smoothly back into...
caption:
Prompt: “Do you have any idea what I want to do to you?”
Pairing: Crowley x Reader

You slid your angel blade smoothly back into your coat, no sign it had ever been out except for the smoking body at your feet. You tossed your hair out of your eyes with a quick flick of your head.

Crowley was standing dumbfounded across the room, starring at you with an expression on his face that you’d only seen before when his best and most devious plans were working.

“What?” you asked.

He didn’t answer for a beat and then paced slowly to close the distance between you to a mere foot. “Do you have any idea what I want to do to you?”

You smiled and bit your bottom lip. “I hope you mean that in a good way,” you replied.

“I mean it in the best and nastiest way,” the King replied.

title: Crowley season 14
body:
So I know that because Mark Sheppard retired officially Crowley is perma-dead but here’s my idea/head canon.

Death brings back Crowley and gives him a new powered up vessel because the demons really need someone to keep them in semi-check. Except the vessel is a woman.

But this changes literally nothing for him. He still wears his suits and goes by king.

Sam is happy to see him for like 5 seconds before Crowley pisses him off by joking that Sam better not think about seducing him because he/she refuses to end up like Sam’s ex-girlfriends.
